{"tid":2093501,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【安全通訊入門】呢兩日見到好多朋友+同事轉用Signal，係好事，但係請唔好用Signal做行動嘢","createTime":"2020-07-04T01:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T01:55:01.000Z","uid":131691,"like":85,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca9270320bf645d05e350a31c99e86a7ed2b055","tid":2093501,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:21:44.000Z","msg":"揀一個安全嘅即時通訊軟件，首先要明白infosec資訊保安裏面，confidentiality保密 同 privacy私隱 係兩樣嘢嚟。<br />\n<br />\nConfidentiality保密：Alice同Bob之間嘅通訊，經手人睇唔到內容，或只會見到亂碼。呢個亦都係end-to-end encryption點對點加密可以做到嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\nPrivacy私隱：Alice同Bob之間嘅通訊，第三者係唔知佢哋通訊咗，或者就算知道Alice有同人通訊，唔知道同邊個通訊，又或者淨係知道有兩個戶口通訊，唔知真人係邊兩個。<br />\n<br />\nSignal係連Snowden都推薦嘅保密通訊軟件，的確係好嘢嚟，但係佢能夠提供嘅係極高嘅confidentiality，但同時犧牲privacy：<strong>因爲Signal係用電話號碼嚟做每個戶口嘅identifier</strong>。亦即係話，<strong>你用Signal做行動嘢，係首先要將你成team人嘅電話號碼入哂落Google/Apple Contacts到。一爆機就全軍覆沒，你點del message都冇用。</strong><br />\n<br />\n可能你會話：咁我成team人用太空卡咪得囉？你咁樣都係玩命，因爲人哋一爆你機，見到嘅就係一堆有可能trace到嘅電話號碼，而唔係一堆電話公司唔會trace到嘅username人物代號。<br />\n<br />\n咁點解Snowden會推薦Signal呢？<strong>又或者，Signal有咩情況會有用呢？</strong>就係當Alice同Bob都唔介意雙方知道對方真人身份嘅時候，想有保密通訊，咁Signal就啱用。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>咁傾行動嘢，有應該用咩呢？</strong>要嘅係一個同時有end-to-end encryption但係又唔使用電話號碼做註冊嘅平台。有人推薦Wickr，但係佢唔係open source所以請唔好用。我之前會推薦Wire，但係佢呢年俾人收購咗，所以都請唔好用。<strong>我而家會推薦Riot.im，佢跨平臺，Android/iOS/Windows/Linux/macOS都有，完全唔使用電話或電郵地址就可以註冊，而且對比起Telegram，Riot.im連group chat都可以開end-to-end encryption。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://about.riot.im/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fabout.riot.im%2F&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IPtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=b0571e0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://about.riot.im/</a><br />\n<br />\n當然，最重要嘅係你部機本身嘅保安都要做得好。仲有安裝支那軟件嘅人（用Redstop共業check），或者用緊小米華爲嘅人，又或者手機密碼同其它密碼一樣嘅人，搞掂嗰啲嘢先啦。"},{"pid":"cbd809dd48e9f0c02a7152c55cf5f31d95538279","tid":2093501,"uid":131691,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:25:57.000Z","msg":"後續：咁係咪唔好用Signal呢？唔係，因爲Signal其實可以完全取代WhatsApp嘅使用情況 &mdash; 一班真人，用真人身份，互相通訊。所以朋友，親戚，同同事之間，如果可以轉用Signal，絕對係好事。"},{"pid":"2d983228bddda0a714b1d6b2eaf246cfc4544bac","tid":2093501,"uid":57575,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"cbd809dd48e9f0c02a7152c55cf5f31d95538279","tid":2093501,"uid":131691,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:25:57.000Z","msg":"後續：咁係咪唔好用Signal呢？唔係，因爲Signal其實可以完全取代WhatsApp嘅使用情況 &mdash; 一班真人，用真人身份，互相通訊。所以朋友，親戚，同同事之間，如果可以轉用Signal，絕對係好事。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:34:35.000Z","msg":"轉用 signal 嘅重點係呢樣<br />\n<br />\nwhatsapp (facebook) 食米田共就大家都知，而家就係要放棄 whatsapp，雖然對 facebook 黎講就算全部香港人唔用 whatsapp 都只係九牛一毛，不過做咗先算<br />\n<br />\n好憎有公司壟斷完就食米田共，apple 係咁，google 係咁，facebook 都係咁<br />\n<br />\n總要有人推倒呢個局面，要記得 google chrome 當初都係用咗好長時間屠龍，而家只係自己變咗龍但係鍾意食米田共"},{"pid":"f99a107b6c2fedac9ca8284f9c9be061c4fb69dd","tid":2093501,"uid":265867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0d3b44256860fd0215f8cec594facf6db0eece","tid":2093501,"uid":131691,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"2d983228bddda0a714b1d6b2eaf246cfc4544bac","tid":2093501,"uid":57575,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"cbd809dd48e9f0c02a7152c55cf5f31d95538279","tid":2093501,"uid":131691,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:25:57.000Z","msg":"後續：咁係咪唔好用Signal呢？唔係，因爲Signal其實可以完全取代WhatsApp嘅使用情況 &mdash; 一班真人，用真人身份，互相通訊。所以朋友，親戚，同同事之間，如果可以轉用Signal，絕對係好事。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:34:35.000Z","msg":"轉用 signal 嘅重點係呢樣<br />\n<br />\nwhatsapp (facebook) 食米田共就大家都知，而家就係要放棄 whatsapp，雖然對 facebook 黎講就算全部香港人唔用 whatsapp 都只係九牛一毛，不過做咗先算<br />\n<br />\n好憎有公司壟斷完就食米田共，apple 係咁，google 係咁，facebook 都係咁<br />\n<br />\n總要有人推倒呢個局面，要記得 google chrome 當初都係用咗好長時間屠龍，而家只係自己變咗龍但係鍾意食米田共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:40:16.000Z","msg":"無錯，所以我其實覺得香港人突然大舉轉用Signal係好事<br />\n但係前提係用Signal取代WhatsApp，唔係用Signal傾行動嘢"},{"pid":"c9fa8464c2ed27a0d99669fb4b3c49a8813f772c","tid":2093501,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7e12e98d702437d38bb1bff561fa0b0bd1f7a2","tid":2093501,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:52:58.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會員標籤功能 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1880412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1880412</a>"},{"pid":"97a0a0d2ae2550cf65ebe9afdd6ee36a6a67895b","tid":2093501,"uid":42981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:03:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31f0c2a943ce917fbf6cdd346e94a6efaf38be0e","tid":2093501,"uid":89879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:03:48.000Z","msg":"singal 當whatsapp 用<br />\nThreema 當 telegram 用"},{"pid":"5712e368785f7ca42d762a01a08aafd3cf864ea2","tid":2093501,"uid":131691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dc7e12e98d702437d38bb1bff561fa0b0bd1f7a2","tid":2093501,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:52:58.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會員標籤功能 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1880412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1880412</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:04:00.000Z","msg":"其實有冇可能將個userscript擺入個webextension到？<br />\n咁樣啲tag就可以用storage.sync令到全部同一個profile嘅Chrome/Firefox可以同步"},{"pid":"78473b18808daa4d426e88bbceed68daf41ff901","tid":2093501,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31f0c2a943ce917fbf6cdd346e94a6efaf38be0e","tid":2093501,"uid":89879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:03:48.000Z","msg":"singal 當whatsapp 用<br />\nThreema 當 telegram 用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:05:19.000Z","msg":"Threema唔係open source，冇得public audit"},{"pid":"39